      <scopecontent id="aspace_84fd6489b63303d0cd348a9e2dab716b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Socialist Party of New Haven records consist of platforms, blank petitions, applications for membership, ballots, tickets, handbills, and open letters of socialist organizations throughout the state of Connecticut. The collection also includes twenty-seven issues of <title render="doublequote">
               <part>The Connecticut Comrade.</part>
            </title>
         </p>  
      </scopecontent>
